    <body><p><seg rend="main_text" rendition="div"><lb />
<seg rend="jisage_3" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 3em">猶南町<seg type="ruby"><seg type="rb">むば</seg><seg type="rp">（</seg><seg type="rt">（乳母）</seg><seg type="rp">）</seg></seg>にもよろしく御伝へ御たのみ申あげ候。</seg>
御文難<seg rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</seg>有、然ニ御<seg type="ruby"><seg type="rb">ちうもん</seg><seg type="rp">（</seg><seg type="rt">（注文）</seg><seg type="rp">）</seg></seg>の銀の板うちの<seg type="ruby"><seg type="rb">かんざし</seg><seg type="rp">（</seg><seg type="rt">（簪）</seg><seg type="rp">）</seg></seg>と云ものに、京打、江戸打と云あり、板打中にも色々の通り在<seg rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</seg>之、画図でも御こしなれバ、わかり可<seg rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</seg>申候。然りといへども後便ニ一つさし出し可<seg rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</seg>申と存じ候。御まち、かしこ。<lb />
<seg rend="jisage_2" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 2em">三月廿四日<seg rend="chitsuki_3" rendition="div" style="text-align:right; margin-right: 3em">龍</seg></seg>
<seg rend="jisage_1" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 1em">呈　ふぐの春猪様</seg>
<seg rend="jisage_8" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 8em">御前へ<seg rend="chitsuki_2" rendition="div" style="text-align:right; margin-right: 2em">龍馬</seg></seg>
<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
</seg></p></body>
